summary: This year I also participate in Printcard exchange project. It's amazing opportunity to get some awesome mini prints from around...
body:
This year I also participate in Printcard exchange project. It’s amazing opportunity to get some awesome mini prints from around the world and show yourself too.

You must send edition of 11 prints. One of them we will present at the exhibition in Wroclaw, and the other 10 we will send in the envelope to the other participants.

Offcial deadline is 31st May (postmark date) & more info on Facebook page 🖖
